  <h2> Who are we? </h2>
<p>
   <%= link_to "Karma", "#jump-to-karma" %> <%= link_to "Grove", "#jump-to-grove"%> is not your average business or charity.  We believe we can make the world better while making tasty treats.  We believe we can make the world better through <i>conscious commerce</i>--empowering the consumer to make a positive, informed, and and predictable impact with the power of their purchase emanating out in the multiplier effect by having a faster velocity of money. 80% of the profits from all transactions in our marketplace are given to charities or community causes. Ten percent is kept for the organization to slowly grow.  Unlike a traditional fundraiser, Karma grove gives both parties involved in the deal a <i>choice</i> of whom the proceeds will benefit.
</p>

<p>
  Karma Grove does not yet facilates conscious commerce through it's marketplace, but it does enable fundraising for charity partners directly through the sale of <b><%= link_to "Karma Coins", "/Karma-Coin" %></b>.
</p>

<br />

<h2> What do we stand for? </h2>

<p>
   The money you exchange for Karma Coins goes directly to a local charities. You decide what charity will benefit from 50% of the sale's proceeds. We believe <i>this is your right</i>, and we apply this same policy to everything you purchase with and from Karma Grove.
</p>
<p>
   As the producer of Karma Coins, our employees pledge the remaining profits to a charity of their own choice. We believe this is their right as the hard-working creators of this delicious treat.  <!-- For more information on donations, <%= link_to "click here", "#" %>. -->
 </p>
 <p>
   Karma Grove is transparent. We're open. We don't keep secrets. All donations made from Karma Coin sales and in the marketplace are tracked and detailed reports our posted here, on our website.
 </p>

